title: War of the Roses: I Saw You On The Boat
description: Amy didn't think much of it when her husband Tom didn't come to fireworks because he was sick last weekend.  But now she's remembering her neighbor mentioning seeing her with Tom at one point when Amy knows she wasn't with him so now she's piecing a few things together wondering if something is going on.
